, die der Wüste das Genick brachen"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Geformt von deinen dunklen, geschickten Händen"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"In der orangefarbenen Hitze des Ofens"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":["Im ",["$","span","1",{"className":"annotation-term border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 cursor-help","title":"Tianshan (Himmelsgebirge) – ein massives Gebirgssystem in Zentralasien, das das Rückgrat und die Lebensader des gesamten Uigurischen Autonomen Gebiets Xinjiang bildet.","children":["Tianshan",["$","sup",null,{"className":"text-xs text-gray-400 ml-px select-none","children":1}]]}],"-Mondlicht"]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"text-xs font-sans font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4","children":"注释"}],["$","ol",null,{"className":"space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"flex text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-xs text-gray-400 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-mono","children":[1,"."]}],["$","span",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-medium text-gray-600","children":"Tianshan"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"mx-1.5 text-gray-300","children":"—"}],"Tianshan (Himmelsgebirge) – ein massives Gebirgssystem in Zentralasien, das das Rückgrat und die Lebensader des gesamten Uigurischen Autonomen Gebiets Xinjiang bildet."]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","Verse aus Dsungarien","》 · ","Band I: Das flackernde Lagerfeuer"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["Li Yu"," / ","1984"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-1-7","className":"max-w-2xl 