h die Kanäle flüstert"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Und irgendwo eine Mundharmonika"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Die eine Melodie aus Shandong spielt"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Hier, unter den Sternen von Junggar"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","Verse aus Dsungarien","》 · ","Band I: Das flackernde Lagerfeuer"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["Li Yu"," / ","1984"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-1-9","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"Lighting a Flickering Campfire — To the Deer"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Here,"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"We light a flickering campfire,"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"And from this shining moment a new epoch of the desert begins;"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"The deer watch from the tamarisk thickets,"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Their eyes catching the firelight;"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"They do not fear us yet,"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"These first pioneers,"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Who smell of earth and sweat"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Rather than gunpowder."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Dear deer — we are your new neighbors,"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"The two-legged creatures"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Who sing off-key by firelight"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"And mean you no harm."}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","Verse aus Dsungarien","》 · ","Band I: Das flackernde Lagerfeuer"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["Li Yu"," / ","1984"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-1-10","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"Einen grünen Traum unter der Düne träumend"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Schon haben wir uns von den Brokat-Reisfeldern verabschiedet"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Schon haben wir uns von den eng beieinanderliegenden neuen Dörfern verabschiedet"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Nicht unsere Jiangnan-Heimat"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Sondern ein Ort, der sich fast wie Heimat anfühlte"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Nun unter der Düne träumen wir einen grünen Traum"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Einen Traum von Obstgärten und Kanälen"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Von Schulen und Kliniken"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Von Kindern, die nur"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Das Grün wachsender Dinge kennen werden"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Nicht das Braun des Marsches"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","Verse aus Dsungarien","》 · ","Band I: Das flackernde Lagerfeuer"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["Li Yu"," / ","1984"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-1-11","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"Heute Nacht überqueren sie erneut die Rotweidenbrücke"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Einst überquerten wir Steinbrücken,"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Einst überquerten wir Einplankenbrücken;"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Wie viele Brücken wir im Laufe eines Lebens überquert haben,"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Doch diese Brücke aus gebündelten Rotweidenzweigen"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Ist diejenige, an die wir uns erinnern werden."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Sie schwankt unter unseren Stiefeln,"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Diese Brücke, die wir selbst gebaut haben"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Aus dem einzigen Bauholz der Wüste,"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Der unzerstörbaren Rotweide."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Heute Nacht überqueren sie erneut die Rotweidenbrücke,"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Auf dem Weg zur Staudamm-Baustelle,"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Auf dem Weg in die Zukunft."}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","Verse aus Dsungarien","》 · ","Band I: Das flackernde Lagerfeuer"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["Li Yu"," / ","1984"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-1-12","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"Trink diese Schale mit Schneeschmelzwasser vom Tianshan"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Die alten Soldaten hießen uns einst auf diese Weise willkommen"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Hießen die neuen Rekruten willkommen, die kamen, um die Wüste zu erobern"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Trink diese Schale mit Schneeschmelzwasser vom Tianshan"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Klar wie Kristall, kalt wie das Herz des Berges"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Das ist unser Wein, unser Begrüßungstrunk"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","ch