 Bagdad nicht zu fern"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["Li Yu"," / ","1984"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-4-8","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"Eine grüne Melodie fließt"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Eine grüne Melodie fließt"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Durch den neu gepflanzten Schutzwaldstreifen,"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Der Wind spielt die Pappeln wie eine Flöte,"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Jeder Baum eine Note in der Partitur."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Ich lausche mit geschlossenen Augen"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Und höre die Zukunft heraus:"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Den Schatten einer ganzen Stadt,"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Die Ruhe einer ganzen Provinz,"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Alles entspringend aus dieser grünen Melodie"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Die als Setzling begann"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"In der Hand eines Soldaten."}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","Verse aus Dsungarien","》 · ","Band IV: Für die Liebe ist Bagdad nicht zu fern"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["Li Yu"," / ","1984"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-4-9","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"O, bitte verlass mich nicht"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"O, bitte verlass mich nicht,"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Nicht jetzt, nicht wenn die Baumwolle kurz davor ist zu blühen,"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Nicht wenn der Stausee fast voll ist,"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Nicht wenn wir fast das Leben aufgebaut haben"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Von dem wir seit Lanzhou sprechen."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Bleib, bis die Pappeln größer sind als wir,"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Bleib, bis die Straße asphaltiert ist,"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Bleib, bis sich die Sterne weniger wie Fremde"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Sondern mehr wie Nachbarn anfühlen."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"O, bitte verlass mich nicht."}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"Die Wüste ist weit genug für zwei."}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","Verse aus Dsungarien","》 · ","Band IV: Für die Liebe ist Bagdad nicht zu fern"]}],"$undefined"]}],["$","p",null,{"